  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://publications.europa.eu/resource/pegase/201023.416691">
    <j.0:event_legal_date rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">2012-03-29</j.0:event_legal_date>
    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="en">The Commission can accept in principle some of the amendments (4 and 24) related to data protection. It has and will defend their spirit during the negotiations in Council. However, the other amendments in this area (3, 6 and 25) do not add clarity but rather confusion and should thus be rejected.</j.0:event_legal_comment>
